page.content: These are a few of the many clubs and societies which advertise on the library notice boards:- Ramblers' Association English Folk Dance and Song Society Townswomen's Guild National Housewives' League Philatelic Society Friends of the Bereaved Intervarsity Club Girl Guide Association Horticultural Society British Federation of University Women Chess Club Natural History Society Historical Society St. John's Ambulance Association Home Organ Society National Childbirth Trust "Body" British Organ Donor Society Watford Life Group Popmobility
